again about moderates.

192
00:12:17,460 --> 00:12:21,330
- Shut up !
- You shut up !

193
00:12:21,350 --> 00:12:23,460
Rafsanjani was a glory hunter !

194
00:12:23,480 --> 00:12:27,320
Rafsanjani was the glue that kept
the whole thing together !

195
