for MailChimp right now, okay ?

197
00:12:32,510 --> 00:12:35,280
John, do you send
a lot of mass emails ?

198
00:12:35,400 --> 00:12:36,480
It's a good podcast.

199
00:12:36,500 --> 00:12:41,320
If you didn't know James Van Der Beek
was an expert in Iranian history,

200
